cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing tasks such as sentiment analysis. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a novel architecture for machine learning models. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it deals with extracting fine-grained opinions from text, and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it utilizes neural networks for its proposed architecture.
